message: /* Awards */ There are lists below.  Look please.  There are three finalists in each location, who are invited to present the project in the final.  Below are those who did not make it to the finals.

Shortlisting means becoming a finalist, being nominated for an award.  Getting to the finals is an achievement; this is a classic practice in all sections of the Awards.  Can be replaced with Finalist.  But I think the nominee is better.  I think that this should be left.
